    "After the signal digital processing, dialect signals as the input of preprocessing.",
    "As shown in Fig. 4, it presents the flow chart of the dialect speech digital processing and preprocessing.",
    "The purpose of preprocessing dialect speech is mainly to clean signals from environmental noises and prepare them for feature extraction.",
    "It includes the following steps (Labied et al. 2022): Voice Activity Detection (VAD), pre-emphasis, framing, and windowing.",
    "VAD can not only be used to mark the starting point and end point of dialect speech signals but also to distinguish between dialect noise and sound areas."
  ],
